South Australia : Spencer Gulf, Port Pirie, Port Noarlunga, Aldinga, Yorke Penninsula, Tiparra Bay, Port Lincoln, Flinders Island , West Island (Peart 2007 a, current study). Western Australia : Cape Riche, Ceduna (current study). Victoria: Gabo Island , Port Philip Bay (current study). New South Wales : Angourie Point, Port Stephens (current study).
